00:01:09.066 --> 00:01:10.926 A:middle
So the telephone has served us

00:01:10.926 --> 00:01:12.616 A:middle
well as customers but it's not

00:01:12.616 --> 00:01:14.406 A:middle
always the most ideal way to

00:01:14.406 --> 00:01:15.566 A:middle
communicate with businesses.

00:01:16.676 --> 00:01:18.036 A:middle
Business Chat is important

00:01:18.036 --> 00:01:19.036 A:middle
because it offers a more

00:01:19.036 --> 00:01:21.076 A:middle
flexible and more capable

00:01:21.076 --> 00:01:21.856 A:middle
experience.

00:01:23.526 --> 00:01:24.986 A:middle
For example, sometimes you're

00:01:24.986 --> 00:01:26.336 A:middle
busy, you're running around.

00:01:26.806 --> 00:01:28.446 A:middle
You need a way to resolve issues

00:01:28.446 --> 00:01:30.066 A:middle
without dedicating your time to

00:01:30.066 --> 00:01:30.696 A:middle
a phone call.

00:01:31.766 --> 00:01:33.076 A:middle
And you definitely don't want to

00:01:33.076 --> 00:01:34.566 A:middle
waste your time waiting on hold.

00:01:35.736 --> 00:01:38.036 A:middle
You need a way to communicate in

00:01:38.036 --> 00:01:39.576 A:middle
between the million other things

00:01:39.576 --> 00:01:41.606 A:middle
that you're doing, a way to

00:01:41.606 --> 00:01:43.406 A:middle
communicate on your schedule.

00:01:44.046 --> 00:01:46.826 A:middle
And a telephone call is not

00:01:46.826 --> 00:01:48.956 A:middle
visual and it's definitely not

00:01:48.956 --> 00:01:50.176 A:middle
as capable as an iPhone.

00:01:51.216 --> 00:01:52.496 A:middle
Sometimes you need to show the

00:01:52.496 --> 00:01:53.876 A:middle
business what you're seeing.

00:01:54.276 --> 00:01:55.526 A:middle
You might have an unfamiliar

00:01:55.526 --> 00:01:58.156 A:middle
product or need help with it or

00:01:58.156 --> 00:01:59.856 A:middle
maybe while you're chatting, you

00:01:59.856 --> 00:02:02.016 A:middle
might need to do something

00:02:02.016 --> 00:02:04.616 A:middle
interactive like choosing from

00:02:04.616 --> 00:02:07.756 A:middle
different options, scheduling an

00:02:07.756 --> 00:02:10.326 A:middle
appointment, making a payment,

00:02:11.216 --> 00:02:13.046 A:middle
or even interacting with an app

00:02:13.836 --> 00:02:15.106 A:middle
and that's Business Chat.

00:02:15.796 --> 00:02:18.606 A:middle
It's a powerful way for

00:02:18.606 --> 00:02:20.006 A:middle
customers to communicate with

00:02:20.056 --> 00:02:22.366 A:middle
you and to complete tasks.

00:02:23.146 --> 00:02:24.000 A:middle
