over the phone.

00:18:47.276 --> 00:18:48.866 A:middle
And it's even way more secure.

00:18:52.786 --> 00:18:54.416 A:middle
Now, you can mix these built-in

00:18:54.416 --> 00:18:56.176 A:middle
features with your own custom

00:18:56.176 --> 00:18:57.826 A:middle
messages apps that you create

00:18:58.976 --> 00:19:00.396 A:middle
and we think there's some real

00:19:00.396 --> 00:19:01.856 A:middle
opportunity here for you to

00:19:01.856 --> 00:19:03.936 A:middle
create some new really amazing

00:19:03.936 --> 00:19:05.346 A:middle
customer engagement experiences.

00:19:06.166 --> 00:19:08.046 A:middle
Now we were so excited about all

00:19:08.046 --> 00:19:09.396 A:middle
of this, we wanted everyone to

00:19:09.396 --> 00:19:11.416 A:middle
be able to try this out today

00:19:11.416 --> 00:19:12.966 A:middle
using your iOS 11 device.

00:19:13.536 --> 00:19:16.826 A:middle
As message app developers, you

00:19:16.826 --> 00:19:18.006 A:middle
can try integrating with your

00:19:18.006 --> 00:19:18.706 A:middle
messages apps.

00:19:19.086 --> 00:19:20.606 A:middle
As customer service platforms,

00:19:20.606 --> 00:19:22.126 A:middle
you can see what formats we're

00:19:22.126 --> 00:19:24.256 A:middle
sending over the wire, or as a

00:19:24.256 --> 00:19:25.636 A:middle
business owner or someone who's

