just interested, you can use the

00:19:27.246 --> 00:19:29.166 A:middle
Sandbox to dream up the next

00:19:29.166 --> 00:19:30.796 A:middle
great customer experience

00:19:30.796 --> 00:19:31.516 A:middle
engagement.

00:19:32.296 --> 00:19:34.696 A:middle
So what did we do?

00:19:35.586 --> 00:19:38.066 A:middle
Well, as Grant showed, we have

00:19:38.326 --> 00:19:39.666 A:middle
this flow of information that

